net.proteusframework.ui.search

Interface JoinedQLBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JoinConditionHelper<JoinedQLBuilder>, QLBuilder

    public interface JoinedQLBuilder
extends QLBuilder, JoinConditionHelper<JoinedQLBuilder>
    A QLBuilder created as a result of calling QLBuilder.createJoin(JoinType, String, String) .

    Implementations should delegate to the root builder if using the QLBuilderImpl. See DelegatingQLBuilder for an example.

    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
